(87, 'Dewgong',     'Water',    'Ice',     1.7,  120.0, 'Loves to snooze on bitterly cold ice. The sight of it sleeping on a glacier was mistakenly thought to be a mermaid.', 90, 70, 80, 70, 95, 70, false, false),
